.SH NAME
App::My::LesspipeUpdate::InstallFile \- update a local lesspipe.sh installation
.SH VERSION
.IX Header "VERSION"
This documentation is for App::My::LesspipeUpdate::InstallFile version 0.1.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 5
\&    use Moo;
\&    use Const::Fast;
\&    use MooX::HandlesVia;
