.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This is an accessory module for App::My::LesspipeUpdate::Update that models
a single file from a build of the lesspipe.sh project and the stow package
file it maps to.
.SH "CONFIGURATION AND ENVIRONMENT"
.IX Header "CONFIGURATION AND ENVIRONMENT"
.SS Properties/attributes
.IX Subsection "Properties/attributes"
\fIinstall_file_path\fR
.IX Subsection "install_file_path"
.PP
The path to an install/build file from built lesspipe.sh project.
.PP
A Types::Path::Tiny::AbsPath object, which can accept a Path::Tiny
object. Required.
.PP
\fIstow_file_path\fR
.IX Subsection "stow_file_path"
.PP
The path to a stow package file that maps to the install/build file defined
in the "install_file_path" attribute.
.PP
A Types::Path::Tiny::AbsPath object, which can accept a Path::Tiny
object. Required.
